Thanks to sNeeP for making awesome map!!
there is soccer with 2 teams (blue and red), Random weapons and nades in cells, some secrets, s4s area, gun toss area, climbing fight (2v2), spray fight, random place losing and dieing, air shotgun (you have to shoot on the blocks to gain attidude and reach the end first), snake game and alot of fun!
